drm/amdgpu: Enable S/G for Yellow Carp

Missing code for Yellow Carp to enable scatter gather - follows how
DCN21 support was added.

Tested that 8k framebuffer allocation and display can now succeed after
applying the patch.

v2: Add hookup in DM

